Gengar (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0093: Haunter
Pokémon
#0095: Onix →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Gengar (TCG Pocket).

Gengar has been featured on 34 different cards since it debuted in the Fossil expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Gengar cards are normally Psychic-type or Darkness-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Gengar

Gengar
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
